query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(dd ss) NoHashJoin(dd ss i) */ select i.i_item_id,
i.i_item_desc,
i.i_category,
i.i_class,
i.i_current_price,
sum(ss.ss_ext_sales_price) AS itemrevenue,
sum(ss.ss_ext_sales_price) * 100 / sum(sum(ss.ss_ext_sales_price)) over (partition by i.i_class ) AS revenueratio
from date_dim AS dd
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_sold_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk AND dd.d_date BETWEEN '1998-03-21'::date AND '1998-04-20'::date
inner join item AS i
on ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk AND i.i_category IN ('Books',
'Shoes',
'Electronics') group by i.i_item_id, i.i_item_desc, i.i_category, i.i_class, i.i_current_price order by i.i_category, i.i_class, i.i_item_id, i.i_item_desc, revenueratio;
